refactor: fix menu not being displayed correctly on other screens after
screen scale ratio

the qt program maintains the topleft's original coordinates after
use scale ratio, but the screen size is scaled. so get the scaling
position of the coordinate point on the current screen, and then
calculate the offset of the upper left corner.
